\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
若 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \phi_{k}\right\} _{k=1}^{N}$
\end_inset

 选取为 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{i}$
\end_inset

 上的
\color red
正交基 (orthogonal basis)
\color inherit

\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\ip{\phi_{k}}{\phi_{l}}\coloneqq\int_{E_{i}}\phi_{k}(\vec{x})\,\phi_{l}(\vec{x})=\ip{\phi_{k}}{\phi_{k}}\delta_{kl},\quad\forall k,\forall l
\]

\end_inset

则 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{A}$
\end_inset

 退化为
\color red
